import { Icon } from '@iconify/react';
import plusFill from '@iconify/icons-eva/plus-fill';
import { Link as RouterLink } from 'react-router-dom';
// material
import {
  Grid,
  Button,
  Container,
  Stack,
  Typography,
  Slider,
  Divider,
  FormGroup,
  FormControlLabel,
  Switch,
  TextField
} from '@mui/material';
// components
import Tooltip from '@mui/material/Tooltip';
import { Box, maxHeight } from '@mui/system';
import React from 'react';
import PropTypes from 'prop-types';
import NumberFormat from 'react-number-format';
import Page from '../components/Page';

//

// ----------------------------------------------------------------------

const marks = [
  {
    value: 0,
    label: '0%'
  },
  {
    value: 20,
    label: '20%'
  },
  {
    value: 40,
    label: '40%'
  },
  {
    value: 60,
    label: '60%'
  },
  {
    value: 80,
    label: '80%'
  },
  {
    value: 100,
    label: '100%'
  }
];

// eslint-disable-next-line prefer-arrow-callback
const NumberFormatCustom = React.forwardRef(function NumberFormatCustom(props, ref) {
  const { onChange, ...other } = props;

  return (
    <NumberFormat
      {...other}
      getInputRef={ref}
      onValueChange={(values) => {
        onChange({
          target: {
            name: props.name,
            value: values.value
          }
        });
      }}
      thousandSeparator
      isNumericString
      allowNegative={false}
      allowEmptyFormatting={false}
      fixedDecimalScale
    />
  );
});

NumberFormatCustom.propTypes = {
  name: PropTypes.string.isRequired,
  onChange: PropTypes.func.isRequired
};

// ----------------------------------------------------------------------

export default function Settings() {
  const [values, setValues] = React.useState({
    numberformat: '255'
  });

  const handleChange = (event) => {
    setValues({
      ...values,
      [event.target.name]: event.target.value
    });
  };
  return (
    <Page title="Settings">
      <Container maxWidth="xl">
        <Stack direction="row" alignItems="center" justifyContent="space-between" mb={5}>
          <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#66fcf1' }}>
            Settings
          </Typography>
        </Stack>
        <Container maxWidth="xl">
          <Grid>
            <Divider>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#66fcf1' }}>
                Speed Settings
              </Typography>
            </Divider>

            <Grid container spacing={{ xs: 10 }} columns={{ xs: 8, sm: 8, md: 8, lg: 8 }}>
              <Grid item xs={2}>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#45a29e' }}>
                  Robot Foward Speed
                </Typography>
                <Slider
                  defaultValue={50}
                  step={10}
                  min={0}
                  max={100}
                  marks={marks}
                  style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2}>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#45a29e' }}>
                  Robot Backwards Speed
                </Typography>
                <Slider
                  defaultValue={50}
                  step={10}
                  min={0}
                  max={100}
                  marks={marks}
                  style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2}>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#45a29e' }}>
                  Robot Turning Speed
                </Typography>
                <Slider
                  defaultValue={50}
                  step={10}
                  min={0}
                  max={100}
                  marks={marks}
                  style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2}>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#45a29e' }}>
                  Acceleration
                </Typography>
                <Slider
                  defaultValue={50}
                  step={10}
                  min={0}
                  max={100}
                  marks={marks}
                  style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                />
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid>
            <Divider>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#66fcf1' }}>
                Lights & Leds
              </Typography>
            </Divider>
            <Grid container spacing={{ xs: 10 }} columns={{ xs: 8, sm: 8, md: 8, lg: 8 }}>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Front Lights 12V
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    color="red"
                    style={{ color: '#fff', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Top Pcb Status LEDs
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Serial Communication LEDs
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Beacon LED
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>

          <Grid>
            <Divider>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#66fcf1' }}>
                Artificial Intelligence
              </Typography>
            </Divider>
            <Grid container spacing={{ xs: 10 }} columns={{ xs: 8, sm: 8, md: 8, lg: 8 }}>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <Tooltip
                  disableFocusListener
                  disableTouchListener
                  title="*This setting will greatly affect CPU & GPU performance & temperatures*"
                >
                  <FormGroup>
                    <Typography
                      variant="h7"
                      gutterBottom
                      style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    >
                      Conversational AI
                    </Typography>
                    <FormControlLabel
                      control={<Switch />}
                      label="OFF/ON"
                      style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    />
                  </FormGroup>
                </Tooltip>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <Tooltip
                  disableFocusListener
                  disableTouchListener
                  title="*This setting will greatly affect CPU & GPU performance & temperatures*"
                >
                  <FormGroup>
                    <Typography
                      variant="h7"
                      gutterBottom
                      style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    >
                      Object Recognition
                    </Typography>
                    <FormControlLabel
                      control={<Switch />}
                      label="OFF/ON"
                      style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    />
                  </FormGroup>
                </Tooltip>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <Tooltip
                  disableFocusListener
                  disableTouchListener
                  title="*This setting will greatly affect CPU & GPU performance & temperatures*"
                >
                  <FormGroup>
                    <Typography
                      variant="h7"
                      gutterBottom
                      style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    >
                      Human Recognition
                    </Typography>
                    <FormControlLabel
                      control={<Switch />}
                      label="OFF/ON"
                      style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    />
                  </FormGroup>
                </Tooltip>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <Tooltip
                  disableFocusListener
                  disableTouchListener
                  title="*This setting will greatly affect CPU & GPU performance & temperatures*"
                >
                  <FormGroup>
                    <Typography
                      variant="h7"
                      gutterBottom
                      style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    >
                      Environment Mapping
                    </Typography>
                    <FormControlLabel
                      control={<Switch />}
                      label="OFF/ON"
                      style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    />
                  </FormGroup>
                </Tooltip>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid>
            <Divider>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#66fcf1' }}>
                Collision & Edge Detection
              </Typography>
            </Divider>
            <Grid container spacing={{ xs: 10 }} columns={{ xs: 8, sm: 8, md: 8, lg: 8 }}>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <Tooltip
                  disableFocusListener
                  disableTouchListener
                  title="*By turning off this setting, the robot may commit suicide*"
                >
                  <FormGroup>
                    <Typography
                      variant="h7"
                      gutterBottom
                      style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    >
                      Front Collision Sensing
                    </Typography>
                    <FormControlLabel
                      control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                      label="OFF/ON"
                      style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    />
                  </FormGroup>
                </Tooltip>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <Tooltip
                  disableFocusListener
                  disableTouchListener
                  title="*By turning off this setting, the robot may commit suicide*"
                >
                  <FormGroup>
                    <Typography
                      variant="h7"
                      gutterBottom
                      style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    >
                      Side Collision Sensing
                    </Typography>
                    <FormControlLabel
                      control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                      label="OFF/ON"
                      style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    />
                  </FormGroup>
                </Tooltip>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <Tooltip
                  disableFocusListener
                  disableTouchListener
                  title="*By turning off this setting, the robot may commit suicide*"
                >
                  <FormGroup>
                    <Typography
                      variant="h7"
                      gutterBottom
                      style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    >
                      Front Edge Sensing
                    </Typography>
                    <FormControlLabel
                      control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                      label="OFF/ON"
                      style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    />
                  </FormGroup>
                </Tooltip>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <Tooltip
                  disableFocusListener
                  disableTouchListener
                  title="*By turning off this setting, the robot may commit suicide*"
                >
                  <FormGroup>
                    <Typography
                      variant="h7"
                      gutterBottom
                      style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    >
                      Back Edge Sensing
                    </Typography>
                    <FormControlLabel
                      control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                      label="OFF/ON"
                      style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    />
                  </FormGroup>
                </Tooltip>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>

          <Grid
            style={{
              overflow: 'hidden'
            }}
          >
            <Divider>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#66fcf1' }}>
                Sensors
              </Typography>
            </Divider>
            <Grid container spacing={{ xs: 10 }} columns={{ xs: 8, sm: 8, md: 8, lg: 8 }}>
              <Grid item xs={1} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Gas
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={1} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Temperature
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={1} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Humidity
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={1} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Tilt
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={1} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Photoresistor
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={1} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Flame
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={1} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Smoke
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={1} style={{ color: '#fff' }}>
                <FormGroup>
                  <Typography
                    variant="h7"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    GPS
                  </Typography>
                  <FormControlLabel
                    control={<Switch defaultChecked />}
                    label="OFF/ON"
                    style={{ alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  />
                </FormGroup>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>

          <Grid container>
            <Grid item xs={5.9} style={{ color: '#fff' }} align="center">
              <Divider>
                <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#66fcf1' }}>
                  Fan PWM Controls
                </Typography>
              </Divider>
              <Grid container spacing={{ xs: 0 }} columns={{ xs: 8, sm: 8, md: 8, lg: 8 }}>
                <Grid item xs={2.6} style={{ color: '#fff' }} align="center">
                  <Typography
                    variant="h5"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Left Fan
                  </Typography>
                  <Box sx={{ height: 90 }}>
                    <Slider
                      orientation="vertical"
                      defaultValue={50}
                      step={10}
                      min={0}
                      max={100}
                      marks={marks}
                      style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    />
                    <Typography
                      variant="h5"
                      gutterBottom
                      style={{ color: '#fff', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    >
                      Intake
                    </Typography>
                  </Box>
                </Grid>

                <Grid item xs={2.6} style={{ color: '#fff' }} align="center">
                  <Typography
                    variant="h5"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Top Fan
                  </Typography>
                  <Box sx={{ height: 90 }}>
                    <Slider
                      orientation="vertical"
                      defaultValue={50}
                      step={10}
                      min={0}
                      max={100}
                      marks={marks}
                      style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    />
                    <Typography
                      variant="h5"
                      gutterBottom
                      style={{ color: '#fff', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    >
                      Exhaust
                    </Typography>
                  </Box>
                </Grid>

                <Grid item xs={2.6} style={{ color: '#fff' }} align="center">
                  <Typography
                    variant="h5"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Right Fan
                  </Typography>
                  <Box sx={{ height: 90 }}>
                    <Slider
                      orientation="vertical"
                      defaultValue={50}
                      step={10}
                      min={0}
                      max={100}
                      marks={marks}
                      style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    />
                    <Typography
                      variant="h5"
                      gutterBottom
                      style={{ color: '#fff', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                    >
                      Intake
                    </Typography>
                  </Box>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>

            <Divider orientation="vertical" flexItem />

            <Grid item xs={5.9} align="center">
              <Divider>
                <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom style={{ color: '#66fcf1' }}>
                  Camera Settings
                </Typography>
              </Divider>
              <Grid
                container
                spacing={{ xs: 0 }}
                columns={{ xs: 8, sm: 8, md: 8, lg: 8 }}
                align="center"
              >
                <Grid item xs={2} align="center">
                  <Typography
                    variant="h5"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Red
                  </Typography>
                  <TextField
                    variant="filled"
                    style={{ maxWidth: '90%', backgroundColor: '#c5c6c7', borderRadius: '10px' }}
                    color="error"
                    helperText="0-255 Range"
                    label="Value"
                    id="RGBInputRed"
                    InputProps={{
                      inputComponent: NumberFormatCustom
                    }}
                    onChange={handleChange}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={2} align="center">
                  <Typography
                    variant="h5"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Green
                  </Typography>
                  <TextField
                    variant="filled"
                    style={{ maxWidth: '90%', backgroundColor: '#c5c6c7', borderRadius: '10px' }}
                    color="success"
                    helperText="0-255 Range"
                    label="Value"
                    id="RGBInputGree"
                    InputProps={{
                      inputComponent: NumberFormatCustom
                    }}
                    onChange={handleChange}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={2} align="center">
                  <Typography
                    variant="h5"
                    gutterBottom
                    style={{ color: '#45a29e', alignSelf: 'center' }}
                  >
                    Blue
                  </Typography>
                  <TextField
                    variant="filled"
                    style={{ maxWidth: '90%', backgroundColor: '#c5c6c7', borderRadius: '10px' }}
                    color="secondary"
                    backgroundColor="#000000"
                    helperText="0-255 Range"
                    label="Value"
                    id="RGBInputBlue"
                    InputProps={{
                      inputComponent: NumberFormatCustom
                    }}
                    onChange={handleChange}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={2} style={{ color: '#fff' }} align="center">
                  <Button
                    color="primary"
                    variant="contained"
                    style={{
                      color: '#fff',
                      fontWeight: 'bolder',
                      fontSize: '1.1em',
                      backgroundColor: '#45a29e',
                      maxWidth: '30px',
                      maxHeight: '30px',
                      minWidth: '150px',
                      minHeight: '75px',
                      top: '38px',
                      boxShadow: 'none'
                    }}
                  >
                    Submit
                  </Button>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </Container>
    </Page>
  );
}
